          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1681817558778-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1681817558778-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1681817558778-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is marinating, peel and grate (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span> </strong>roughly</p><p>Heat a pot with a lid on a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!), <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground turmeric </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1681817563394-x200.jpg",
