          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681817571447-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until lightly browned</p><p>Transfer the <strong>browned chicken</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (reserve the pan!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-14 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>peri-peri chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817579043-x200.jpg",
