      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, stir the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> through the <strong>cooked rice</strong> – this is your <strong>spiced rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>peri-peri chicken </strong>with the <strong>spiced rice</strong>,<strong> punchy peas </strong>and <strong>perinaise </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
